Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.35,0:00:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作为地球其中的一个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.73,0:00:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥布就有义务协助联合军
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.33,0:00:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.27,0:00:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后通谍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.44,0:00:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.95,0:00:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望借此机会下船的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.93,0:00:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请尽快离舰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.12,0:00:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,依照奥布政府的指示进行避难
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.44,0:00:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.01,0:00:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为这是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然奥布选择的道路是最艰难的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.79,0:00:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基..基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.16,0:00:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以要...知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.99,0:00:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是帅啊 反正我还只是新兵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.98,0:00:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.83,0:01:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freedom 基拉?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.08,0:01:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰你是以什么信念去战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.58,0:01:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是荣获的勋章? 还是父亲的命令?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.15,0:03:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(600,600)\fs33\fscy130\b0}PHASE-37 阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helldart 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:03:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚沙琪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.01,0:03:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二防卫线已经被突破
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.39,0:03:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和第六机械中队 联系中断
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.10,0:04:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 你这家伙是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃 还有啊 奇怪的M.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.90,0:04:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是隶属ZAFT特殊部队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰·萨拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.94,0:04:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能听见吗 Freedom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是基拉·大和吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.28,0:04:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么意图
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ZAFT想要介入这场战争吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我并未接到有关这场战争的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此次介入
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我个人的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管他的 连你一起干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.08,0:05:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么 多了一架
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.56,0:05:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥尔加 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.66,0:06:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.35,0:06:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是别的联合军的机体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是 是在掩护Freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.41,0:06:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在玩什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少碍事 奥尔加
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.23,0:06:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏尼 你这混帐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.83,0:07:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.64,0:07:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.72,0:07:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左转舵20 消灭左边的舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,休想过去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.26,0:07:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,数量多也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.89,0:07:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茱莉!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:08:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没有占领军队总部吗 真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您自豪的新机体好像没有预料中的作为啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必杀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.59,0:08:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥尔加!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.91,0:08:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.32,0:08:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏尼 你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙连同伴都打
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.52,0:08:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烦人的是你 奥尔加
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混帐 到时间了 Clotho 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.68,0:09:11.62,type,,0000,0000,0000,,Raider、Forbidden、Calamity : 地球军新开发的原型机体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.68,0:09:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raider Forbidden还有Calamity返回
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.22,0:09:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.81,0:09:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.26,0:09:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了 稍微休息下 舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暂时撤退 全军撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:48.12,type,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike Dagger:地球军首批量产的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正只靠Strike Dagger也做不了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥布的实力比预想中的强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.68,0:09:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是没有他们就去战斗的话 会全灭的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发射信号弹 暂时撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.81,0:10:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你的掩护
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.02,0:10:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我想再次确认你的真意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.81,0:10:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从本国接到夺回或击毁那架机体 Freedom的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.55,0:10:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对你和你的友军没有敌对的意图
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.17,0:11:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你..谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.68,0:11:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.90,0:11:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,军医 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,补给快点 敌人就要再发动攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.72,0:11:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伤者送去那边帐篷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.82,0:11:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送配给过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.67,0:11:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左脚不行了 拿锯来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.24,0:12:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用担架了 拿装尸袋来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 左臂在这
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家 干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道他们撤退的理由...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.88,0:12:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候的ZAFT兵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.69,0:12:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.62,0:13:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.17,0:14:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.78,0:14:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托利?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.98,0:14:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.32,0:14:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡..卡嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们这俩混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.08,0:15:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.79,0:15:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道很困难
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.73,0:15:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 没有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,认为卡嘉莉的父亲所说的 是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.79,0:15:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是奥布站在地球军那边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.46,0:15:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大西洋联邦就会利用这力量攻击PLANTs
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果站在ZAFT那边也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是敌人变了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.60,0:15:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样没有用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.71,0:15:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再那样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.04,0:16:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.76,0:16:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我杀了你的同伴 朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.84,0:16:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不认识他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并不是我想要杀他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你杀了Tolle
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你不认识Tolle
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并不是想要杀了他 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.57,0:16:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾想要杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.25,0:16:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.74,0:16:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是在没有战斗的世界就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.18,0:16:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能一直生活在那样的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.21,0:17:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 战争在不断扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.91,0:17:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了赢得胜利 这是我们需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.58,0:17:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那能量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.58,0:17:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,PLANTs和地球真的只有彼此相互毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.51,0:17:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.45,0:17:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为即使是保护他人 我已经开过枪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.91,0:17:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们又会彼此战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.74,0:17:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.17,0:18:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我是敌人的话 你会开枪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ZAFT的阿斯兰·萨拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.97,0:18:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要回去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.52,0:18:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道什么时候会再发动攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要问你个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.79,0:18:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freedom搭载了Neutron Jammer Canceller
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.06,0:18:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个数据 你...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.65,0:18:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是有人想拿走另有所图的话 我会杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.71,0:18:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.71,0:18:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀了Tolle的那个人是他...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.33,0:18:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以想怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:18:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没听到基拉说的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.33,0:19:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.71,0:19:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀了他Tolle就能回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.71,0:19:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会的 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.82,0:19:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.55,0:19:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个...等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.03,0:19:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还要多久才能完成准备
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥布再三发出会谈的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那已经太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的战力都不能攻下的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是让它消失最好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.98,0:19:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们这边的准备就快好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问题是你那边的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那还真是失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:20:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就再次开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.55,0:20:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惩罚应该已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次再不好好干的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.93,0:20:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就连示威的目的都达不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.18,0:20:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要一直跟着我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.72,0:20:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别在意 只是在监视
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.52,0:20:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.43,0:20:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉还活着 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.84,0:20:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候 我还没道谢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有的 算是谢过了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.29,0:20:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.76,0:20:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时你心不在焉 或许不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.52,0:20:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.50,0:20:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 变了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.28,0:20:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.16,0:20:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.70,0:21:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是那样子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.47,0:21:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊...那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.48,0:21:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今后打算怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.81,0:21:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.65,0:21:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又来了...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.91,0:21:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是或许已经有答案了...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.77,0:21:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很痛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.62,0:21:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.42,0:21:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追加了十个单位的Gilpeptin
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.45,0:21:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2个小时内没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.29,0:21:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想再受苦的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.20,0:21:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次就好好的干
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.31,0:21:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.88,0:21:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.27,0:22:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那两架机体
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.55,0:22:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.73,0:22:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打下来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.59,0:23:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遮住双眼的是困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.29,0:23:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盖住耳朵的是愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.57,0:23:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而还是会映出那看过的脸庞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.37,0:23:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那听过的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.87,0:23:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 思绪无法传达
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.11,0:23:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逼近的黑暗如此深重
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.16,0:23:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被逼进的是更加艰苦的道路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.74,0:23:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集 机动战士Gundam Seed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.68,0:23:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞向拂晓的宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.74,0:23:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在此名下冲破它吧 Gundam
